description	"Archetype: Dark Pursuer

Class: Sith.
Class Summary: 
A highly aggressive Sith that excels in flanking due to enhanced movement and swing speed. 

Lightsaber Staff:
- Defense (2)
- Deflect (2)
- Increased reach
- Can use Yellow and Staff styles

Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (3)
- Pull (2)
- Grip (2)
- Sense (2)
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (2)

~Character Option 1: Darth Maul - Former apprentice of Darth Sidious, Maul is a relentless killer - whose single-minded hatred motivates and sustains him.
~Character Option 2: Second Sister - Once the Jedi Padawan Trilla Suduri, the Second Sister was an Inquisitor hunting remnants of the Jedi Order after the Purge.
~Character Option 3: Empress Rey Palpatine - A vision of evil taken form. 
~Character Option 4: Darth Zannah - The successor to Darth Bane who murdered him to carry on his teaching of 'The Rule of Two.'"
